{"word":"παραλλάξ","slug":"παραλλάξ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παραλλάξ</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:παραλλάσσω'><el>παραλλάσσω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>alternately, in turn</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>vicissim</el>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>in alternating rows</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>ad quincuncem dispositi</el>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}